'''过氧化物酶体'''（{{lang-en|'''peroxisome'''}}）是一种被称为{{le|酶体|Microbody}}的[[细胞器|细胞器]]，几乎存在于所有[[真核生物|真核]]细胞中<ref name="pmid20124343">{{cite journal | vauthors = Gabaldón T | title = Peroxisome diversity and evolution | journal = Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society of London. Series B, Biological Sciences | volume = 365 | issue = 1541 | pages = 765–73 | date = Mar 2010 | pmid = 20124343 | pmc = 2817229 | doi = 10.1098/rstb.2009.0240 }}</ref>。它们参与{{le|非常长链脂肪酸|Very long chain fatty acid}}，{{le|支链脂肪酸|Branched chain fatty acids}}，[[氨基酸|D-氨基酸]]和[[多胺|多胺]]的[[异化作用|异化作用]]，[[活性氧类|活性氧类]]的还原-尤其是[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]]<ref name="ROS and peroxisomes">{{cite journal | vauthors = Bonekamp NA, Völkl A, Fahimi HD, Schrader M | title = Reactive oxygen species and peroxisomes: struggling for balance | journal = BioFactors | volume = 35 | issue = 4 | pages = 346–55 | pmid = 19459143 | doi = 10.1002/biof.48 | year=2009}}</ref>-以及{{le|缩醛磷脂|Plasmalogen}}的生物合成，即{{le|醚磷脂|Ether lipid}}-对于哺乳动物大脑和肺的正常功能至关重要<ref name="pmid16756494">{{cite journal | vauthors = Wanders RJ, Waterham HR | title = Biochemistry of mammalian peroxisomes revisited | journal = Annual Review of Biochemistry | volume = 75 | issue =  | pages = 295–332 | year = 2006 | pmid = 16756494 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.biochem.74.082803.133329 }}</ref>。它们还含有大约10％的在[[戊糖磷酸途径|戊糖磷酸途径]]中两种酶全部活动，这对能量代谢很重要<ref name="pmid16756494"/>。关于过氧化物酶体是否参与[[类萜|类萜]]和动物[[胆固醇|胆固醇]]合成的争论很激烈<ref name="pmid16756494"/>。 其他已知的过氧化物酶体功能包括发芽种子中的[[乙醛酸循环|乙醛酸循环]]（“glyoxysomes”），叶子中的[[光呼吸|光呼吸]]<ref>{{cite book | vauthors = Evert RF, Eichhorn SE | year = 2006 | title = Esau's Plant Anatomy: Meristems, Cells, and Tissues of the Plant Body: Their Structure, Function, and Development|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=9780471738435}}</ref>，锥虫中的[[糖酵解|糖酵解]]（“{{le|糖酵解酶体|glycosome}}(glycosome)”），以及某些酵母中的[[甲醇|甲醇]]和/或胺氧化和同化。

過氧化體用外表的單層膜與細胞的[[原生質|原生質]]分隔開來，膜上有功能重要的[[膜蛋白|膜蛋白]]，用以向細胞器中輸入[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]和促進[[細胞分裂|細胞分裂]]。與[[溶酶體|溶酶體]]不同的是，過氧化物酶體不是由[[分泌通路|分泌通路]]產生，而是通過先長大後分裂的自我複製過程產生，也有證據顯示新的過氧化物酶體可以直接產生{{請求來源}}。

== 历史 ==
过氧化物酶体在1967年被[[比利时|比利时]]细胞学家[[克里斯汀·德·迪夫|克里斯汀·德·迪夫]]（Christian de Duve）鉴定为细胞器<ref name="pmid4389648">{{cite journal | vauthors = de Duve C | title = The peroxisome: a new cytoplasmic organelle | journal = Proceedings of the Royal Society of London. Series B, Biological Sciences | volume = 173 | issue = 1030 | pages = 71–83 | date = Apr 1969 | pmid = 4389648 | doi = 10.1098/rspb.1969.0039 }}</ref>；在此之前的1954年过氧化物酶体首先被一位瑞典博士生 J. Rhodin 所描述<ref name="Rhodin_1954">{{cite journal | vauthors = Rhodin, J | title = Correlation of ultrastructural organization and function in normal and experimentally changed proximal tubule cells of the mouse kidney | journal = Doctorate Thesis. Karolinska Institutet, Stockholm | volume = | issue =  | pages =  | year = 1954 | pmid = | doi =  }}</ref>。

== 代谢功能 ==
过氧化物酶体的主要功能是通过[[β-氧化|β-氧化]]分解{{le|非常长链脂肪酸|Very long chain fatty acid}}。在动物细胞中，长脂肪酸转化为中链[[脂肪酸|脂肪酸]]，随后转运至[[线粒体|线粒体]]，最终分解为二氧化碳和水。在酵母和植物细胞中，这一过程仅在过氧化物酶体中进行<ref name="alberts">{{cite book | vauthors = Alberts B,  Johnson A, Lewis J, Raff M, Roberts K,  Walter P | title = Molecular Biology of the Cell | edition = Fourth | publisher = Garland Science | location = New York | year = 2002 | pages = | quote = | isbn = 0-8153-3218-1 | chapter  = Chapter 12: Peroxisomes | url = https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/bv.fcgi?rid=mboc4.section.2194 | accessdate = }}</ref>。

== 其他相关的细胞器 ==
与过氧化物酶体相关的其他微生物家族的细胞器包括在植物和[[霉菌|丝状真菌]]的[[乙醛酸循环体|乙醛酸循环体]]，在[[动质体|动质体]]的[[糖酵解酶体|糖酵解酶体]]<ref name="pmid1447292">{{cite journal | vauthors = Blattner J, Swinkels B, Dörsam H, Prospero T, Subramani S, Clayton C | title = Glycosome assembly in trypanosomes: variations in the acceptable degeneracy of a COOH-terminal microbody targeting signal | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-cell-biology_1992-12_119_5/page/1129 | journal = The Journal of Cell Biology | volume = 119 | issue = 5 | pages = 1129–36 | date = Dec 1992 | pmid = 1447292 | pmc = 2289717 | doi = 10.1083/jcb.119.5.1129 }}</ref>，和在[[霉菌|丝状真菌]]的[[伏鲁宁体|伏鲁宁体]]（Woronin body）。

